<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Day 1: Create Your First Post</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .step-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        }

        .step-number {
            background-color: #667eea;
            color: white;
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Day 1: Create Your First AI-Powered Post</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi <%= name %>,</h2>

            <p>You're 5 minutes away from your first viral-worthy LinkedIn post! Here's your simple 3-step process:</p>

            <div class="step-box">
                <span class="step-number">1</span>
                <strong style="color: #333;">Choose a Topic</strong>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 40px;">Share an insight from your industry, a lesson learned, or a trending
                    topic</p>
            </div>

            <div class="step-box">
                <span class="step-number">2</span>
                <strong style="color: #333;">Pick a Viral Hook</strong>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 40px;">Our AI will suggest attention-grabbing opening lines</p>
            </div>

            <div class="step-box">
                <span class="step-number">3</span>
                <strong style="color: #333;">Let AI Work Its Magic</strong>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 40px;">Get a complete, engaging post ready to publish in seconds</p>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%=  %>/dashboard/post-generator"
                    class="cta-button">
                    Create My First Post â†’
                </a>
            </div>

            <div
                style="background-color: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 30px 0;">
                <strong style="color: #856404;">Pro Tip:</strong>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #856404;">The best-performing posts are authentic and provide
                    value. Share your unique perspective - that's what makes your content stand out!</p>
            </div>

            <p><strong>What to expect tomorrow:</strong><br>
                We'll show you how to create a custom AI persona that writes in YOUR voice.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Let's make your first post amazing!<br><strong>The Engagematic Team</strong>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> Engagematic. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= preferencesUrl %>">Email Preferences</a> |
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>